# Add these dependencies to package.json:

```json
"dependencies": {
  ...existing dependencies...,
  "react-beautiful-dnd": "^13.1.1",
  "@mui/icons-material": "^5.14.0"
}
```

```json
"devDependencies": {
  ...existing devDependencies...,
  "@types/react-beautiful-dnd": "^13.1.4"
}
```

# Then run:
npm install
